Text: Re GIR SettlementSkaff is no longer with Crosby Heafey Roach and May Please direct any email to his new address Thanks Brian Transwestern Pipeline Company asks that it be included on list of parties to the Motion for Modification of the Procedural Schedule with the following footnote Transwestern supports the portions of the settlement proposal pertaining to transmission rights and the designation of primary and secondary rights described on Appendix A Transwestern does not oppose the other parts of the settlement Susan Scott Transwestern Pipeline Company
